<h1>Thanks for reaching out</h1>

<p>Hi<%= " #{@name.split.first}" if @name %>,</p>

<p>
  Thanks for your interest in HCB. We've got your note, and someone from our
  team will reach out personally — usually within a day — to learn what you're
  looking to fund and how we can help you deploy it.
</p>

<% if @message %>
  <p style="color: #8492a6; margin-bottom: 4px;">What you shared:</p>
  <blockquote style="margin: 0; padding: 12px 16px; border-left: 3px solid #ec3750; background: #f9fafc;">
    <%= simple_format @message %>
  </blockquote>
<% end %>

<p>
  In the meantime, just reply to this email if there's anything you'd like us to
  know.
</p>

<p>
  Talk soon,
  <br>
  The HCB team
</p>
